I"â<div class="p">Drum, beats the drum in the rickshawed tower;</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The drumbeat echoes through my soul.</div>
<div class="p">Drum, beats the guilty footprint of sinners</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Madly circling Dubarry's bowl.</div>
<div class="p">Drum, beats the sentence of heaven's council;</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; No hope remains for pride and sin.</div>
<div class="p">Drum, beats the thunder in the pagan skies,</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A most unloving sort of din.</div>
<div class="p">Drum, beats the lord of the lilting bosom,</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The marrow of man's other self.</div>
<div class="p">Drum, beats the hailstorm of the father slain;</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Children thrust 'pon charity's shelf.</div>
<div class="p">Drum, beats the future on Normandy's shore;</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A precious symphony we hold.</div>
<div class="p">Drum, beats the shadow in Lucy's corner,</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The deathless tale of honor told.</div>
<div class="p">Drum, beats the terrible breath of Typhon,</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; As gods before his fire flee.</div>
<div class="p">Drum, beats the Bay when the Phlegethon breaks</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; And Naples touches Sicily.</div>
<div class="p">Drum, beats the engine on the gate of Troy:</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Helen's beauty there to regain.</div>
<div class="p">Drum, beats the circling hand of Cassandra;</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; It strikes the twelfth hour amain.</div>
